## Where I Am Honestly At

I want to be straightforward about where I stand relative to CGRC readiness. Nineteen days into this challenge I have solid conceptual grounding in most of the domains. What I am still building is:

- Deeper hands-on experience with control implementation — particularly in AWS
- Practical understanding of what a real control assessment looks like
