The remaining 81 days of this challenge are designed to address exactly those gaps. By the end of the 100 days I want to have worked through a complete GRC lifecycle for OpenMRS — from scoping and categorization through control selection, implementation, assessment, and authorization. That end-to-end experience is what will make the CGRC a realistic next step rather than an aspirational one.

